// useState - props and state control
// useEffects - creates side effect (take note, this is outside the logic loop)
// useContext - pass the value to different components - application is best in usernames
// useCallback - applied to specific component that only need changing so that it will not rerender the entre DOM (simply caches a function)
// useMemo - caches values so that when the same result appeared, it will not take longer for the output to be displayed. 


